name: 2023 7th International Conference on Sustainable Energy Engineering
content: Publication: All papers submitted to the conference will be subjected to the rigorous peer-review process. ICSEE 2023 all accepted papers will be pubished into \*Springer Book Series-Green Energy and Technology\*, which submitted for \*Ei Compendex\*, and \*Scopus\* and are expected to be widely read and cited.
